Sync, protect, and share. Everywhere.

Copy is a syncing client that offers 15gb of 
space for free. It works on x86, x86_64 and 
armv6h. It also includes a command line client 
called CopyConsole.

The main executable is called CopyAgent.

You may use this link to receive an additional 
5gb for free (totaling 20gb):
https://copy.com?r=TxbyWL
